      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:21:9",
      "text": [
        " قُلْتُ لِأَبِي عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) مُحْرِمٌ قَبَّلَ غُلَاماً مِنْ شَهْوَةٍ قَالَ يُضْرَبُ مِائَةَ سَوْطٍ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Yahya Bin Al Mubarak, from Abdullah Jabala, from Is’haq Bin Ammar who said, ",
          "‘I said to Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup>, ‘One in <span class=\"iTxt\">Ihraam</span> kissed a boy from desire’. He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘He would be whipped one hundred lashes’."
        ]
      }
